item.title: How do I code customs like Vestas, and other pk armour [317]
item.dc:creator: @LilXCj LilXCj
item.description:
@LilXCj wrote:

I’d much rather you find them on your own. That way you feel much more proud of yourself when you get them to work. It’s all in the process of becoming a java programmer. Good luck! If you need help on specific things that can’t be answered by searching this site or google, I’d be happy to answer.

Except for client-sided things. I don’t work with client-sided thing.
